{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/Nephilim-Logo.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Nephilim</i> is a student-made isometric combat and exploration game set in a dying fantasy land. As Strider Lazarus, you'll learn to master both Light and Shadow to vanquish the foes standing in your path. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/Steam_Headers_Shadows__1_.png?t=1738375693\" />Switch between the Light and the Dark worlds to empower your abilities, get over obstacles and solve puzzles.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/Shadowmesh.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/Steam_Headers_Dash.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/NephilimLS_920.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight Angels and Demons alike using all the tools in your arsenal! You'll need to master everything to defeat the game's many bosses.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast and Charged attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Special unlockable combos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Powerful Light and Dark Ultimate Abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Holy Sword Summon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speed is of the essence. Move quickly to evade attacks, Health Potions can run out quick!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/Steam_Headers_Explore.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/CheckpointMenu.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Keep your eyes peeled for Upgrade Gems. Each one takes you one step closer to being to ultimate warrior. Invest them at Bonfires to increase Strider Lazarus' stats and to unlock new combos, attacks and special abilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Nephilim</i> was made over 4 months  by a team of six developers and features an original soundtrack by <i>Nerveight</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738375693","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738375693","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/47e1d46c2f1bfead5fbcf1055d7de8c2317621e5/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738375693","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/47e1d46c2f1bfead5fbcf1055d7de8c2317621e5/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738375693","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3381510/extras/Nephilim-Logo.png?t=1738375693\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Nephilim</i> is a student-made isometric combat and exploration game set in a dying fantasy land. As Strider Lazarus, you'll learn to master both Light and Shadow to vanquish the foes standing in your path. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite